title: #92Noon! Warren/Span/Leber/Tafoya/Birk/Flacco/Wiggs
description: Big 10 Commish Kevin Warren starts the show for a couple segments, and Denard Span ends the first hour...Leber in for two mid way thru, followed by Michele Tafoya...Final hour features Matt Birk with teammate and SBXLVII MVP Joe Flacco, then Birk sticks around to chat with former Vikings teammate and SB winner with the Patriots, Jermaine Wiggins!
